佢就冇啦啦沖左水彈到我成個屎忽都濕哂"},{"pid":"424f35634b7e46300c7ab850827844ed9e0ef3d7","tid":435883,"uid":24160,"like":12,"dislike":6,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T22:53:03.000Z","msg":"其實有食肉菌嗰個case <br />\n喺街市公廁啲排水系統同衞生又差<br />\n先至令鹹水會有咁多菌..<br />\n加上事主年紀大抵抗力差啲<br />\n先會容易感染嘅<br />\n<br />\n如果樓主係後生, <br />\n唔係街市呀,政府公廁<br />\n又唔係直接畀海水或者污糟鹹水濺到傷口<br />\n應該冇乜大礙嘅<br />\n<br />\n同埋最重要係<br />\n記冚蓋沖, 如果係自動沖嘅話<br />\n就自己一屙完就起身離開廁所沖<br />\n<br />\n再有疑惑就去睇醫生做個check up 啦<br />\n洗費求安心都要㗎"},{"pid":"6b1693c8f7550dd745c1f34cc29c7823b32c7c83","tid":435883,"uid":32619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T23:00:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>習慣屙屎擺定廁紙係底 防彈水 <br />\n唔記得上網邊度搵返嚟</blockquote><br />\nsame<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而且痾果陣會冇咁大聲 唔洗驚尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我唔係彈水花，係佢直程自動感應沖廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我一郁佢就冇啦啦沖左水彈到我成個屎忽都濕哂</blockquote><br />\n即係成個屎忽都要切 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eeabeb79585f190fac2d7457dfaf3dacf511daf","tid":435883,"uid":5181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T23:03:27.000Z","msg":"高登仔傳統技能咁撚快就失傳左啦？<br />\n仲要話鋪紙巾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e409fd9fc81a4ae2d1395dbdb8291115374376f","tid":435883,"uid":15497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T23:49:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"185285233a3431e0f1c8d48b076d5fd2a5bec8a8","tid":435883,"uid":119508,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T23:52:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-XNDM4eAn1U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-XNDM4eAn1U&d=fVwol9U6Yy0EO7sgrY9iKp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=6d680684\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-XNDM4eAn1U</a>"},{"pid":"9ba31f2e0c6dcaec0b97940509c7c63487806995","tid":435883,"uid":3476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T23:55:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好似要切菊保命？</blockquote><br />\n菊要點切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n切片？"},{"pid":"1729f58c0613e5e773f2ba68d9847a948a59fa5b","tid":435883,"uid":3488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T23:56:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>防彈少年臀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"833b65c89cf2e9038427e173e819d5fe457fdcd7","tid":435883,"uid":151833,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T00:52:00.000Z","msg":"由細到大 出街痾屎就算幾急都會擺陣先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e271e86811e14b5422fca22e552bf84123d254c4","tid":435883,"uid":65298,"like":7,"dislike":21,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T01:02:26.000Z","msg":"創傷弧菌，俗稱食肉菌，是一種常活於和暖海水的細菌。若傷口接觸海水，或進食被該細菌污染的食物，可引致感染，即壞死性筋膜炎。<br />\n<br />\n基本上一感染左，就一定要切，乜野即時洗傷口消毒都冇用，只係切多定係切少。中左呢隻仆街菌，如果及時去醫院檢查，可能切舊受感染既肉出黎就冇事，但如果等佢十幾個鐘都唔理，基本上一定要截肢。順帶一提，感染後嘅死亡率係30%。<br />\n<br />\n咁就講番我嘅故事啦，幾年前我同班fd去沙灘游水，其中一個女仔原本都冇傷口，但上岸時跌親，跪左一跪落舊石度擦損左，咁就即時洗傷口再消毒貼膠布啦，之後佢都冇再落水，玩完大家番歸。<br />\n<br />\n點知第二朝佢隻腳已經腫到上膝頭，即時去睇醫生，入左ICU，醫生話一定要切，如果唔係會死，佢死都唔肯，果佢家人呀男朋友呀同我地就去勸佢切，果陣佢喊到呼天搶地咁款，真係好心up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我諗唔到講咩好，醒起佢男朋友係信耶穌，就同佢講話係神嘅考驗，神閉背你一道門，必為你開一扇窗，點知佢喊得仲犀利，最後佢男朋友同佢講話無論佢變成點都好，都唔會離開佢，咁終於勸服佢去做截肢<br />\n<br />\n無啦啦冇左隻腳要坐一世輪椅，佢由原本陽光女孩變到好消極，原本讀梗year3退左學，收埋自己係屋企，直到有日佢男朋友捉佢落街一齊番教會做見證，得到教會弟兄姊妹嘅祝福，漸漸地由男朋友捉佢落去變成自己落去<br />\n<br />\n番左教會之後，佢成個人都渙然一新，比出事之前更加開朗，係神嘅見證下同男朋友結婚，仲一齊做埋傳道人，向教友分享神嘅恩典，通過小小一個考驗，就可以令一個對上旁反感嘅人變得依賴上帝，你地話上帝係咪好偉大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c61a2b3bc64933b9bb7b3914c455fa45c798000","tid":435883,"uid":37522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T01:10:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好似要切菊保命？</blockquote><br />\n菊要點切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n切片？</blockquote><br />\n環切，轉人做肛門"},{"pid":"b2eeaf2618898d51105d8035658e967a3d92a5d5","tid":435883,"uid":67289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T01:42:04.000Z","msg":"即刻揾人幫你奶乾淨屎眼"},{"pid":"2dc0542768eb9ea43b0843dcf55e215825913a45","tid":435883,"uid":117786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T02:12:00.000Z","msg":"D細菌n手<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7918e2cb1c0b5f3fb931e399da331316a66707a7","tid":435883,"uid":111293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T02:21:38.000Z","msg":"RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"